{"tid":499181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李慧琼叫保安沒收邵家臻發聲裝置　毛孟靜報稱不適","createTime":"2017-12-14T13:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T13:40:39.000Z","uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"433e1bbc53bdc14bd2ae583387c0016b3d771c07","tid":499181,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T13:40:39.000Z","msg":"立法會正在審議修改《議事規則》議案。議員邵家臻發言結束前，稱要叫醒一些正在沉睡的人，並拿出發聲裝置，發言結束後仍繼續響鬧。代主席李慧琼要求保安拿走發聲裝置，其間邵家臻傳給其他議員。眾人一度與保安糾纏，另一議員毛孟靜報稱不適。<br />\n<br />\n議員黃定光稱為毛健康着想，建議送她入醫院。李慧琼下午約5時半表示，為送毛孟靜離場，會議一度暫停。復會後，毛孟靜重新列席，隨即要求點算法定人數，然後起身離開會議廳。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171214/s00001/1513244208343\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171214%2Fs00001%2F1513244208343&d=6QxlN6fDmcXkHnYsSNDSXP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=e30879a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171214%2Fs00001%2F1513244208343&h=7818e78b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171214/s00001/1513244208343</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">片段(1:00 注意音量):</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KNv2M7X43tM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKNv2M7X43tM&d=6QxlN6fDmcXkHnYsSNDSXP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=78958a1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KNv2M7X43tM</a>"}]}